								<foliation>
									<p>479 folios (+ 1unfoliated parchment flyleaf).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>61 quires: i2 (folios 1-2), ii-lx8 (folios 2a-473), lxi8-2 (folios 474-479). </p>
									<p>Catchwords at the end of the quires.</p>
								</collation>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="15" writtenLines="15">
									<p>Uniform layout.</p>
									<p>Hair side and flesh side are distinguishable. </p>
									<p>Ruling is visible. There are 15 lines in the body of a page and 22 in the margin.</p>
									<p>Initial words are written in larger characters.</p>
									<p>Catchwords are given at the end of the quires.</p>
									<p>Blank pages: folios 1v, 2r, [2a recto] and [2a verso].</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
